apine)." Boehringer-Ingelheim, Ridgefield, CT.[6] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0[7] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[8] "Product Information. Coartem (artemether-lumefantrine)." Novartis Pharmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.', 1767365203);
