anover, NJ.[4] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0[5] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[6] "Product Information. Coartem (artemether-lumefantrine)." Novartis Pharmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.', 1767365203);
