n Product Information." O 0[7] "Product Information. Coartem (artemether-lumefantrine)." Novartis Pharmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.[8] Wohlt PD, Zheng L, Gunderson S, Balzar SA, Johnson BD, Fish JT "Recommendations for the use of medications with continuous enteral nutrition." Am J Health Syst Pharm 66 (2009): 1438-67[9] "Product Information. VFEND (voriconazole)." Pfizer U.S. Pharmaceuticals, New York, NY.[10] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0[11] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[12] "Product Information. Coartem (artemether-lumefantrine)." Novartis Pharmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.', 1767365203);
